      <p class="sub">referred to as "BAIC Group"</p>
      <p class="desc">BAIC Group is a pillar enterprise in China's automotive industry. Founded in 1958, it has evolved into a large-scale enterprise group with a comprehensive industrial chain covering vehicle and component R&D and manufacturing, automotive service and trade, integrated mobility services, finance and investment, generating annual revenue exceeding RMB 480 billion.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- S3: VIDEO kv3 -->
  <section class="s-video" id="vidSec3" onclick="toggleVid(this,'vid3')">
    <video id="vid3" muted loop playsinline preload="metadata">
      <source src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/video/kv3.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="play-overlay"><div class="play-circle"></div></div>
  </section>

  <!-- S4: CORE BUSINESS -->
  <section class="s-core fade-in">
    <h2>CORE BUSINESS</h2>
