      </div>
      <div class="s-core-item">
        <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/arcfox.png" alt="ARCFOX">
        <p>ARCFOX delivered 81,017 units, up 169.91% from the previous year.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="s-core-item">
        <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/fukuda.png" alt="Foton">
        <p>BAIC Foton achieved total sales of 614,000 units with a market share of 15.8%.</p>
      </div>
