    <h2>SOCIAL RESPONSIBILITY</h2>
    <div class="s-social-imgs">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/page9_rainwater.png" alt="">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/page9_ocean.png" alt="">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/aboutUs/ecp/page9_hill.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <p>Since 2016, BAIC has always implemented the people-oriented concept. while operating, it has always focused on fulfilling corporate social responsibilities and actively carried out social welfare activities.</p>
    <p>In Uganda, Mexico, South Africa, Central and Western Asia and other places, the volunteer spirit of "dedication, friendship, mutual assistance, and progress" has been practiced by donating to schools, earthquake relief, poverty alleviation, and environmental protection.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- S11: CHARITABLE ACTIVITIES TITLE (marquee) -->
  <section class="s-charity-banner fade-in">
    <h2>Charitable Activities Walking with Love</h2>
    <div class="s-marquee"><span>BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;BAIC BLUE PLAN&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div>
  </section>

  <!-- S12: CLOSING STATEMENTS -->
  <section class="s-closing fade-in">
    <p>Driving harmonious development of people, vehicles, and nature through technological innovation</p>
    <p>BAIC is committed to sustainable development management</p>
    <p>Working hand in hand with internal and external stakeholders</p>
    <p>Maximizing comprehensive value for society, economy, and environment</p>
    <p>Dedicated to becoming a model of sustainable development through technology and environmental stewardship</p>
  </section>

</div>

@section Scripts {
<script>
// Video toggle play
function toggleVid(section,vidId){
  const v=document.getElementById(vidId);
  if(v.paused){v.play();section.classList.add('playing')}
  else{v.pause();section.classList.remove('playing')}
}

// Auto-play videos when scrolled into view
const vidObs=new IntersectionObserver((entries)=>{
  entries.forEach(e=>{
    const v=e.target.querySelector('video');
    if(!v) return;
    if(e.isIntersecting){v.play();e.target.classList.add('playing')}
    else{v.pause();e.target.classList.remove('playing')}
  });
},{threshold:0.4});
document.querySelectorAll('.s-video,.s-vid2').forEach(el=>vidObs.observe(el));
</script>
}
